rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Lilio and the others are in the
middle of intense training.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Watching them struggle
through their salvaging
practice got me all fired up.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0003
rows.name:
No, wait. That makes me sound
like a dangerous person.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Watching them overcome hardship,
grow, and improve their salvaging
skills got me all fired up.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0005
rows.name:
It makes me want to raise
them to be even better.
